      <title>美联储会议纪要显示，多位官员认为有必要降息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-21/fed-minutes-show-several-officials-saw-case-for-rate-cut</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在美联储 7 月 30 日至 31 日的会议上，几位美联储官员承认降息是合理的，但美联储政策委员会最终一致投票决定维持利率不变。Mike McKee 报道。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-21/fed-minutes-show-several-officials-saw-case-for-rate-cut</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 21 Aug 2024 18:34:21 GMT</pubDate>
