      <title>Enbridge 在新竞争中削减石油管道系统通行费</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-21/enbridge-cuts-tolls-on-oil-pipeline-system-amid-new-competition</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于阿尔伯塔至温哥华新管道的建设，竞争加剧，Enbridge Inc. 削减了加拿大石油出口管道的收费。]]></description>
