    <item>
      <title>交易员关注降息路径，欧元飙升至一年高点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-21/euro-surges-to-one-year-high-as-traders-eye-interest-rate-path</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧元兑美元升至一年来最高水平，因为货币交易员押注美国央行行长将在杰克逊霍尔美联储经济研讨会上强调降低借贷成本的理由。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-21/euro-surges-to-one-year-high-as-traders-eye-interest-rate-path</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 21 Aug 2024 15:47:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>阿根廷将与美国签署协议以促进金属投资</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-21/argentina-to-join-us-group-for-spurring-metals-investments</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国国务院官员表示，阿根廷将与美国签署一项协议，以吸引更多关键矿产开采领域的投资和贸易，这是美国正在进行的加强不涉及中国的金属供应链的努力的一部分。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-21/argentina-to-join-us-group-for-spurring-metals-investments</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 21 Aug 2024 13:50:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美联储会议纪要提振降息预期，股市上涨：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-20/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美联储公布最新会议纪要且美国非农就业数据大幅下调，增强了市场对美联储官员将在9月份降息的预期，股市和债市因此走高。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-20/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
